#: ../../theory/performance.rst:2
msgid "Prediction Performance"
msgstr "预测性能"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:5
msgid "Generalization Capability"
msgstr "泛化能力"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:7
msgid ""
"Although trained exclusively on three-dimensional bulk crystals from the MP "
"database, DeePAW demonstrates remarkable zero-shot generalization "
"capability:"
msgstr "尽管训练仅使用来自 MP 数据库的三维体相晶体，DeePAW 仍表现出显著的零样本泛化能力："

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:9
msgid "**3D Crystals**"
msgstr "**三维晶体**"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:11
msgid ""
"Good predictive performance on unseen three-dimensional perfect crystals "
"outside the MP database"
msgstr "在 MP 数据库之外未见过的三维理想晶体上仍具有良好预测性能"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:12
msgid ""
"Capable of handling crystal structures containing point defects (vacancies, "
"interstitial atoms, and substitutional atoms)"
msgstr "能够处理含点缺陷（空位、间隙原子与替位原子）的晶体结构"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:13
msgid ""
"Successfully applied to large supercells containing 154 atoms per unit cell "
"(e.g., V4C6B144)"
msgstr "已成功应用于每个晶胞含 154 个原子的超大超胞体系（例如 V4C6B144）"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:15
msgid "**Low-Dimensional Materials**"
msgstr "**低维材料**"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:17
msgid "Two-dimensional materials: monolayer structures (e.g., CsF monolayer)"
msgstr "二维材料：单层结构（如 CsF 单层）"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:18
msgid ""
"One-dimensional materials: nanotube structures (e.g., carbon nanotubes)"
msgstr "一维材料：纳米管结构（如碳纳米管）"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:20
msgid "**Application Scenarios**"
msgstr "**应用场景**"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:22
msgid ""
"Catalysis research: analysis of surface oxygen evolution reaction (OER) "
"pathways (e.g., Na-doped RuO2)"
msgstr "催化研究：表面析氧反应（OER）路径分析（如 Na 掺杂 RuO2）"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:23
msgid ""
"Ferroelectric materials: polarization charge density analysis of "
"orthorhombic-phase HfO2"
msgstr "铁电材料：正交相 HfO2 的极化电荷密度分析"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:24
msgid ""
"Interstitial site discovery: prediction of energetically favorable "
"interstitial occupation sites based on charge density"
msgstr "间隙位点发现：基于电荷密度预测能量有利的间隙占位位置"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:27
msgid "Supported Material Types"
msgstr "支持的材料类型"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:32
msgid "Material Type"
msgstr "材料类型"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:33
msgid "Support Level"
msgstr "支持级别"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:34
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:35
msgid "Oxides"
msgstr "氧化物"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:36 ../../theory/performance.rst:39
#: ../../theory/performance.rst:42
msgid "Full support"
msgstr "完全支持"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:37
msgid "Abundantly represented in the training set"
msgstr "在训练集中覆盖充分"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:38
msgid "Metals and Alloys"
msgstr "金属与合金"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:40
msgid "Covers a wide range of metallic elements"
msgstr "覆盖广泛的金属元素"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:41
msgid "Semiconductors"
msgstr "半导体"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:43
msgid "Includes Group IV, III-V, and related compounds"
msgstr "涵盖 IV 族、III-V 族及相关化合物"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:44
msgid "2D Materials"
msgstr "二维材料"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:45 ../../theory/performance.rst:48
#: ../../theory/performance.rst:51
msgid "Zero-shot generalization"
msgstr "零样本泛化"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:46
msgid "Not present in training set but predictable"
msgstr "训练集中未出现但可进行有效预测"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:47
msgid "1D Materials"
msgstr "一维材料"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:49
msgid "Nanotube and related structures"
msgstr "纳米管及相关结构"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:50
msgid "Defect Structures"
msgstr "缺陷结构"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:52
msgid "Vacancy, interstitial, and substitutional defects"
msgstr "空位、间隙与替位缺陷"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:53
msgid "Molecular Structures"
msgstr "分子结构"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:54
msgid "Partial support"
msgstr "部分支持"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:55
msgid "Requires periodic boundary conditions"
msgstr "需要周期性边界条件"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:58
msgid "Known Limitations"
msgstr "已知局限"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:60
msgid ""
"The coverage of training data is limited by the availability of KSDFT "
"calculations in the MP database"
msgstr "训练数据覆盖范围受 MP 数据库中 KSDFT 计算可得性的限制"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:61
msgid ""
"Predictive accuracy may degrade for elemental combinations that are "
"underrepresented in the training set"
msgstr "对于训练集中覆盖不足的元素组合，预测精度可能下降"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:62
msgid ""
"Molecular structures require the manual imposition of periodic boundary "
"conditions"
msgstr "分子结构需要手动施加周期性边界条件"

#: ../../theory/performance.rst:63
msgid ""
"For certain elements, inconsistent POTCAR usage within the dataset may cause"
" errors in the total electron count during inference; fine-tuning on a case-"
"by-case basis may be necessary"
msgstr "对于某些元素，数据集中 POTCAR 使用不一致可能在推理时引起总电子数误差；必要时需按具体体系进行微调"
